"(define (fp-pin-header ct)
  ;; available ct: 1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8
  (kicad-helper "Connector_PinHeader_2.54mm.pretty/"
                (~a "PinHeader_1x"
                    (~r ct #:min-width 2 #:pad-string "0")
                    "_P2.54mm_Vertical.kicad_mod")))

(define (fp-pin-header-2 ct)
  (kicad-helper "Connector_PinHeader_2.54mm.pretty/"
                (~a "PinHeader_2x"
                    (~r ct #:min-width 2 #:pad-string "0")
                    "_P2.54mm_Vertical.kicad_mod")))"
